articles.title: "Black Panther: Wakanda Forever" tops the North American box office - Africanews English
articles.description: The film "Black Panther: Wakanda Forever" continued its reign at the top of the North American box office, raking in more than $64 million over the Thanksgiving long weekend, according to figures from trade firm Exhibitor Relations on Sunday.
